import React, {Component} from 'react'
import {Container, Row, Col} from 'reactstrap'

class RegisterForm extends Component {
    state = {
        email: "",
        firstname: "",
        lastname: "",
        fullName: "",
        password : "",
        passwordConfirm : "",
        phoneNumber : "",
    }
    render(){
        return(
            <React.Fragment>
                <Container fluid>
                    <Row lg={2}>
                        <Col>
                            <input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="First Name"/>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Last Name"/>     
                        </Col>
                       
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col xs={12} lg={{span: 3, offset : 3}}>
                            <input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Email"/>  
                            <input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Password"/>  
                            <input style={inputStyle} type="text" placeholder="Confirm Password"/>  
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Container>
            </React.Fragment>
        )
    }
}
const inputStyle = {
    padding: "10px",
    margin: "10px",
}
export default RegisterForm
